title: Former legendary Colts kicker Adam Vinatieri earns Pro Football HoF honors

sources.title: Former legendary Colts kicker Adam Vinatieri earns Pro Football HoF honors
sources.description: Arguably the greatest ever to do it at his position, former legendary Colts kicker Adam Vinatiri will be enshrined into the Hall of Fame during the summer of 2026.
